  "description": "Phase-21 follow-up to Phase-20 finding 2 (the 16-sign distributional cluster is enriched 2.5x at site-prefix 510000 = Banawali/Rakhigarhi). This graph stratifies M77 by Mahadevan site_code prefix (Mohenjo-daro / Harappa / Lothal / Kalibangan / Banawali / Other) and computes the bigram-transition spectral gap per site group. If site groups exhibit materially different spectral signatures (spread >= 0.10), the M77 corpus encodes a regional/dialectal component, not a single uniform script grammar. Output: reports/phase21b_site_stratified.json.",
